[section#exec.get.compl.sched
    [`execution::get_completion_scheduler]
]

[para]
[:en] The name [`get_completion_scheduler] denotes a query object template.
[:zh_CN] 名字 [`get_completion_scheduler] 代表一个查询对象模板。

[para]
[:en] Let [*completion-fn] be a completion function ([#exec.async.ops]);
let [*completion-fn-tag] be the associated completion tag of [*completion-fn];
let [`args] and [`envs] be packs of subexpressions; and
let [`sndr] be a subexpression such that [`[`:c sender]<decltype((sndr))>] is [`true] and
[`get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>(get_env(sndr), envs...)]
is well-formed and denotes a scheduler [`sch].
[:zh_CN] 令 [*completion-fn] 为一个完成函数（[#exec.async.ops]）；
令 [*completion-fn-tag] 为 [*completion-fn] 的关联完成标签；
令 [`args] 和 [`envs] 为子表达式的包组；并令 [`sndr] 为子表达式，使得
[`[`:c sender]<decltype((sndr))>] 为 [`true]，并使得
[`get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>(get_env(sndr), envs...)]
良构且代表调度器 [`sch]。

[para]
[:en] [`get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>] obtains the completion
scheduler associated with a completion tag from a sender[=']s attributes.
[:zh_CN] [`get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>] 获得于发送器属性中的
完成标签关联的完成调度器。

[para]
[:en] For subexpression [`sch1] and pack [`envs], let [`sch2] be
[`[*TRY-QUERY](sch1, get_completion_scheduler<set_value_t>, envs...)] and
let [`[*RECURSE-QUERY](sch1, envs...)] be expression-equivalent to [`sch1]
if [`sch2] is ill-formed or if [`sch1] and [`sch2] have the same type and compare equal;
otherwise, [`[*RECURSE-QUERY](sch2, envs...)].
[:zh_CN] 对于子表达式 [`sch1] 和包组 [`envs]，令 [`sch2] 为
[`[*TRY-QUERY](sch1, get_completion_scheduler<set_value_t>, envs...)]，并且
如果 [`sch2] 非良构或者 [`sch1] 和 [`sch2] 具有相同类型且比较相等，则令
[`[*RECURSE-QUERY](sch1, envs...)] 按表达式等价于 [`sch1]；否则
按表达式等价于 [`[*RECURSE-QUERY](sch2, envs...)]。

[para]
[:en] For a subexpression [`q] and pack [`envs], the expression
[`get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>(q, envs...)]
is ill-formed if [*completion-fn-tag] is not one of
[`set_value_t], [`set_error_t], or [`set_stopped_t].
[:zh_CN] 对于子表达式 [`q] 和包组 [`envs]，如果 [*completion-fn-tag] 不是
[`set_value_t]、[`set_error_t] 或 [`set_stopped_t] 之一，那么表达式
[`get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>(q, envs...)] 非良构。

[:en] Otherwise, the expression is expression-equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 否则，该表达式按表达式等价于：
[list]
[item]
[codeblock]
[[redoc("*>")]]MANDATE-NOTHROW([[redoc("*>")]]RECURSE-QUERY(
  [[redoc("*>")]]TRY-QUERY(q, get_completion_scheduler<[[redoc("*>")]]completion-fn-tag>, envs...), envs...))
[codeblock:end]
[:en@~] if that expression is well-formed, except that [`envs...] is evaluated only once.
[:zh_CN@~] 如果该表达式良构，但 [`envs...] 只求值一次。
[item]
[:en] Otherwise, [`auto(q)] if the type of [`q] satisfies [`:c scheduler] and
[`envs] is not an empty pack, except that [`envs...] is evaluated.
[:zh_CN] 否则，如果 [`q] 的类型满足 [`:c scheduler] 并且 [`envs] 不是空包组，
则为 [`auto(q)]，但 [`envs...] 被求值。
[item]
[:en] Otherwise, [`get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>(q, envs...)] is ill-formed.
[:zh_CN] 否则，表达式 [`get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>(q, envs...)] 非良构。
[list:end]

[para:mandates:~]
[:en] If [`get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>(q, envs...)]
is well-formed, its type satisfies [`:c scheduler].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>(q, envs...)] 良构，
则其类型满足 [`:c scheduler]。

[para]
[:en] For a type [`Tag], subexpression [`sndr], and pack [`envs], let [`CS] be
[`completion_signatures_of_t<decay_t<decltype((sndr))>, decltype((envs))...>].
[:zh_CN] 对于类型 [`Tag]、子表达式 [`sndr] 和包组 [`envs]，令 [`CS] 为
[`completion_signatures_of_t<decay_t<decltype((sndr))>, decltype((envs))...>]。

[:en] If both [`get_completion_scheduler<Tag>(get_env(sndr), envs...)] and
[`CS] are well-formed and [`CS().[*count-of](Tag()) == 0] is [`true],
the program is ill-formed.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`get_completion_scheduler<Tag>(get_env(sndr), envs...)] 和
[`CS] 都良构，并且 [`CS().[*count-of](Tag()) == 0] 为 [`true]，则程序非良构。

[para]
[:en] If an asynchronous operation created by connecting [`sndr] with a receiver
[`rcvr] causes the evaluation of [`[*completion-fn](rcvr, args...)],
the behavior is undefined unless the evaluation happens on an execution agent
that belongs to [`sch][=']s associated execution resource.
[:zh_CN] 如果由连接 [`sndr] 和某个接收器 [`rcvr] 所创建的异步操作导致求值
[`[*completion-fn](rcvr, args...)]，则除非求值发生于某个属于 [`sch] 的关联执行资源
的执行代理中，否则其行为未定义。

[para]
[:en] The expression [`forwarding_query(get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>)]
is a core constant expression and has value [`true].
[:zh_CN] 表达式 [`forwarding_query(get_completion_scheduler<[*completion-fn-tag]>)]
是核心常量表达式且值为 [`true]。
